                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                                        <sic>\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">Obitury</hi>\n                                        </sic>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>Died at <placeName>Elizabeth Port. New Jersey</placeName> on\n                                                  <date>22d<lb/> Hisvan 5612</date> corresponding\n                                        with the <date>17<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> November<lb/>\n                                                  1851</date>. <persName>David Bair</persName>, Son\n                                        of <persName>Mr. Abraham Bair</persName><lb/> and Grand Son\n                                        of <persName>Mr David Haar</persName>, aged<lb/> One year\n                                        and nine months, his <sic>corpes</sic> was<lb/> taken to\n                                                  <placeName>Williams Burg</placeName> and there\n                                        entered<lb/> in the <sic>Portagues</sic> new\n                                                  <sic>Buriel</sic> ground, he was<lb/> a fine and\n                                        sensible child, peace be to his<lb/> departed soul - - -\n                                                  <persName role=\"author\"><hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                                  >Benjamin Lindo</hi></persName></p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
